lines.text: Forget it, Derry. Okay? Just forget it! There's nothing you have to say that interests me anymore.

[sees Diana from a distance]
I wanna marry her and have 37 children.

[to Bobby]
Just wanna see her naked.

[to Derry]
Go away. Take your hair for a walk!

[to Mike]
You know, I can never use my father's lines on a girl like that?

[to Bobby]
Just wanna see her naked.
Mike, this is a team, and... and Robert is the quarterback of that team!
[Bobby, dressed as Roberta, chatting with sorority women from afar]
A team is a synergistic unit; it is... a symbiotic system; it is an integrated whole.
If that whole develops a hole, it becomes...
